{"tid":2063752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：貿易戰美國不會是贏家","createTime":"2020-06-14T09:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T00:53:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":44,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"926ee750c2c20d429d79681975746c86ca8158b7","tid":2063752,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/06/14/2494044_60b435bc4a57bfdbe5d1ae874314e8f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F06%2F14%2F2494044_60b435bc4a57bfdbe5d1ae874314e8f4.jpg&h=82645b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華接受鳳凰衞視訪問時表示，美國與香港的貿易關係屬互惠互利，任何傷害將屬於雙向性，不會有贏家。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，個別國家無論是限制別人到當地提供服務，或限制自己的企業到其他國家或城市服務，定必令自身經濟條件轉差，美國與香港的貿易關係屬互惠互利，兩地在高端專業服務業更是「你中有我，我中有你」，任何風吹草動，包括傷害，均屬於雙向性，不會有贏家。<br />\n<br />\n他又相信，很多旅遊行為和方式在疫情過後均可能有所改變，屆時要先起動本地旅遊、消費較高的商貿旅遊，以及能豐富旅客某方面知識和經驗的「有增值」和「主題式」旅遊。在應付疫情的過程中，當局累積很多實際經驗，例如把會展服務變成網上展覽，香港可透過5G的低接觸、高效的連接方式，與全世界的貿易夥伴連成一體。<br />\n<br />\n他直言，「有危就有機」，香港要把握疫情帶來的商機，繼續朝智慧城市方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華說，國家推出港區國安法是出於憲制要求及實際需要，填補因《基本法》第二十三條未立法而出現憲法上的空隙，由於投資者均重視社會是否穩定和安全，立法可以為所有投資者帶來信心和安穩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2494044&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=c8eb046d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494044</a>"},{"pid":"beb28dbbec107f3fb89ebc8b41daa9c896974b8a","tid":2063752,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73825c0134ebcb4ac47ce91cc18fd63d15edef26","tid":2063752,"uid":30040,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:19:13.000Z","msg":"中國恐成最大贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5643eb396e8b37d34ad6b78561caacf7890abfc6","tid":2063752,"uid":281347,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"又「好心」忠告對家？"},{"pid":"93dd3978555fe1f35b3da9924cd764b71421aa67","tid":2063752,"uid":264245,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"今日咁撚多狗官打飛機，打得最大好似係佢"},{"pid":"020f72a08a85c8611d0c2d94066911b6fb6ff85d","tid":2063752,"uid":248131,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"你老頂都未出聲咁快衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3005a75576ac1f49175e7cafa9d5f6a3a5e4d2eb","tid":2063752,"uid":58552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"你邊位呀"},{"pid":"e6e09479d15421806ebb8e035ac4a33a7f694f5f","tid":2063752,"uid":61161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5596e51d50ba885dbe56265283c39c2772574952","tid":2063752,"uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"但中國一定是輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b55d5aeeddabe3ac257de30ca7c5525ae549b6","tid":2063752,"uid":34189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"獨立關稅係基本法賦予，香港一定係最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6183bb4a31e70ecafdbe80e5db569395d91c336","tid":2063752,"uid":254450,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"支持邱生再企硬d，直接屌柒美國不識時務，拎石砸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg